sequenceDiagram
participant User
participant API
participant Facade
participant PlaceModel
participant DB

User->>API: GET /places
API->>Facade: get_places(filters)
Facade->>PlaceModel: fetch places
PlaceModel->>DB: SELECT * FROM places
DB-->>PlaceModel: places data
PlaceModel-->>Facade: list of places
Facade-->>API: return places
API-->>User: 200 OK (places list)